# AI RAG Project Standards - STRICTLY ENFORCED

## 🚫 FORBIDDEN TECHNOLOGIES
❌ NO Langchain, LlamaIndex, or other LLM frameworks
❌ NO SQLite, MySQL, ChromaDB, Pinecone, or other databases
❌ NO Flask, Django, or other web frameworks
❌ NO Claude, Cohere, or other LLM providers

## ✅ MANDATORY TECH STACK
- **API**: FastAPI + Pydantic v2 ONLY
- **LLM**: OpenAI GPT-5/mini/nano ONLY
- **Embeddings**: text-embedding-3-small ONLY
- **Database**: PostgreSQL + pgvector ONLY
- **Monitoring**: Langfuse ONLY
- **Workers**: Celery/RQ + Redis ONLY

## 📁 PROJECT STRUCTURE - ENFORCED
```
app/
├── agents/          # AI agent implementations
├── api/            # FastAPI routes and main app
├── core/           # Configuration and utilities
├── infra/          # Infrastructure (db, llms, vectors)
├── schemas/        # Pydantic models
└── services/       # Business logic
```

### Code Quality Checks:
```bash
uv run ruff check . --fix          # Must pass
uv run ruff format .               # Must pass
uv run black . --check             # Must pass
uv run mypy . --strict             # Must pass
```

### Required Elements:
- ✅ **Type hints**: 100% coverage on all functions/methods
- ✅ **Error handling**: Try-catch blocks in all service methods
- ✅ **Logging**: Structured logging for all operations
- ✅ **Docstrings**: All classes and public methods documented
- ✅ **Validation**: Pydantic models for all API input/output
- ✅ **Async/Await**: All I/O operations must be async

### Naming Conventions:
- **Files**: `snake_case.py`
- **Classes**: `PascalCase`
- **Functions/Variables**: `snake_case`
- **Constants**: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`

## 🚨 IMMEDIATE REJECTION CRITERIA
Code will be **immediately rejected** for:
- Missing type hints
- Using forbidden technologies
- Hardcoded values (use config)
- Missing error handling
- Code duplication
- Breaking project structure
- Direct database access from API
- Missing documentation
